{"id": "jos032", "name": "Audio_Base_702_09_30", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Xenon_Studio", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "What is this place?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "The basement of the Cafe... More commonly known as \"The Exchange\".\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Simon, what I'm about to tell you is everything that I have done here, in this very location, all of it.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Got it. Go ahead.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... This thing started all the way back with pops...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... And just like that, all the transactions take place here. Even until now, this cafe is still offering the same services, operating among the gangs...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "I've never had a person to repent my crimes to. This business was passed down to me by pops. I acknowledged his ideals too... To be honest, I'm not even certain if this is something I need to repent... The only thing I know for sure is that I f***ed up big time...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "After hearing all that... you find me despicable as well, don't you...?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... It is indeed despicable.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Haha... As expected... I don't mind that either. I realized that a long time ago, and I've already prepared myself to live the rest of my life shouldering all the guilt...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Ugh!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punchs", "Consecutive Punches"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Arghhhh!!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I'm the sole person that you can repent to, right? Then the only person you need to feel guilty towards is me. I felt really p***ed off after hearing you talk about those things, so I punched you. I feel much better now after giving you a smackdown.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Now we're even.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Huh? Hey, you promised me that you'll make the right decision, one that you truly believe in...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Yes, and I just did. Afterward, if I ever remember these things and still feel p***ed off, I'll come here and punch you again. I will punish you in place of those who suffered because of your actions. All you need to do is shut up and take my punches like a man.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Ha... So is this the punishment I'm getting?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "The underground punisher, didn't you ask if I was interested to make a comeback? Well, here I am.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Haha... Okay, you win... By the way, what kind of puny punch was that? It barely tickled me.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Then how about I treat you to a few more of them?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "...... N, no thanks......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... JOE, about the human trafficking you just mentioned, there's a little girl with the name \"Ringo\", right? That just so happens to be related with the case I'm investigating.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "For real!?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Yes. I gave it some thought... About the situation between you and the Baro gang, I can't really do much from my current position. They are way too big of an organization for me to take on...\nHowever, at the very least, I can help solve the case of this little girl first.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "How are you going to do that? Diego and Co. cover their tracks very well. If any information leaks, they'll immediately suspect that I was involved...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Rest assured. The legendary \"X\" has returned. Let me handle this. I will not let the lines be traced back to you.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Simon, thank you.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "The heck? This is so unlike you. Besides, I now have free punches to throw at your face whenever I feel like it. Don't thank me so soon.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "No, I am truly grateful to you... I've been under this immense pressure for such a long time, to the point where I can barely breathe. It's like the devil is clamping my heart in its claws... It's making me hysterical... Even my mom is really worried about me. I feel so much better after pouring my heart out to you...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Oof!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "This punch is \"You're welcome\".\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "...... You really should work out more.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Shut up.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Oh, right. You said... that the incident with big sis may have something to do with the things I just said. What's all that about?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Yeah...... Sherry, Luis, Shannon... as well as my father's death; they may all be related to this human trafficking group.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Eh!?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I was able to track this group down afterward. This is an organization whose roots were from Node 03 and have existed for multiple decades already. I think \"Mogura\" is the name. It's highly possible that 03's Administration Bureau has been infiltrated by them as well... Human trafficking is one of their largest businesses.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Are you saying that big sis is...?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Here's my personal view on all this...\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Xenon_Studio", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ここはなんだ？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Cafeの地下室……いわゆる「取引所」だ。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Simon、俺は今から、この場所で俺がしてきたこと、全部お前に話す。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……あぁ、分かった。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……親父は生きてた頃……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……ってこと。\n取引は全部ここでやってきた。\n今に至るまでずっと、このカフェは、カフェであるのと同時に、やくざのために動く場所でもあるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "ずっと、懺悔できる相手がいなかった。\nこの仕事は、親父が俺に託したんだ。\n俺もあの人の考えには賛同してる……\nもう、このこと自体が懺悔するべきことなのかどうなのかすら分からないんだ……\n今俺に分かるのは、俺はやべーってことだけだよ……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "俺のこと……最低な人間だって思っただろ……？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……そうだな。最低だ。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "はは……やっぱね……うん、いいんだ。\nこの罪悪感を一生背負って生きてく覚悟はできてるから……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "グハッ！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punchs", "続けて殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "うああ！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "俺は、お前が唯一懺悔できる相手だろ？\nお前は俺にだけ罪悪感を抱いていればいい。\nさっき、お前の話を聞いて、ムカついた。\nでも、今、お前を殴って、スッキリした。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "これでおあいこだ。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……は？\nなぁ、自分が正しいと思う決断を下すって約束したよな……？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あぁ、その通りにした。\nこれからも、この事を思い出してムカつくことがあったら、またお前を殴る。\nお前のせいで不幸になった人たちの代わりにな。\nお前は黙って俺に殴られてればいい。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "はっ……これが俺がウケるべき制裁かよ？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「地下の制裁者」、また俺にやって欲しいんじゃないのか？\n帰ってきたぞ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "はは……負けたよ、お前には……\nてかさ、さっきの拳なんだよ？\n痛くもかゆくもねぇんだけど。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "そうか？\nなら、あと数発いっとくか。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……いえ、結構です……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……JOE、さっきの話にあった人身売買だが、「Ringo」と呼ばれる女の子がいたんだよな？\nちょうど、俺が調べてる件に関係がある。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "まじ！？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あぁ、ちょっと考えさせてくれ……\nお前とバローの状況を考えると、俺が下手に何かするわけにはいかないな。\n奴らはあまりにもデカすぎる……\nだが、その女の子のことくらいは、何とかできるかもしれない。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "どうするつもりだ？\nDiegoは上手く隠してる。\nもし少しでも情報が漏れれば、すぐに俺だって分かるはずだ……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "安心しろ、俺は「X」だ。\n「X」が帰ってきた。\n俺に任せろ。お前に迷惑はかけない。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Simon、ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "なんだお前。気持ち悪いぞ。\nそれに、俺は今好きな時に好きなだけお前を殴る権利を手に入れたんだ。\n礼を言うのは早いんじゃないか？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "いや、それでもありがとう……\nずっとプレッシャーに押しつぶされそうだった……\n悪魔に心臓を握られてる気分だったんだ……\nヒステリックになって、母さんにも心配かけてた。\n全部話したら、すごい楽になったよ……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "グハッ！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "これは「どういたしまして。」だ。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……もっと鍛えた方がいいぞ。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "黙れ。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……そうだ。\n姉御のことが俺の話に関係あるかもって言ってなかったか？\nどういうことだよ？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あぁ……Sherry、Luis、Shannon……それから、俺の父親の死は、全部この人身売買グループと関係があるかもしれない。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "え！？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "俺の調べによると、これはNode03に10数年も前から深く根付いている組織らしい。\n名前は「土竜」。\nおそらく、03の管理局もやつらに侵食されている……\nそして、人身売買はやつらが力を入れている商売のひとつだ。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "まさか姉御がなんて言わないよな……？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……俺の考えを話す……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Xenon_Studio", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這是什麼地方？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Cafe 的地下室……俗稱「交易所」。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Simon，現在開始，我會把所有我在這裡做過的事情，都告訴你。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……嗯，說吧。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……其實老爹以前……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……就是這樣，所有的交易都是在這裡發生的。一直到現在，這間咖啡廳也還以相同的功用在黑幫間運作著……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我一直沒有能懺悔的對象，事業是老爹交給我的，我也認同他的理念……甚至連這本身是不是件該懺悔的事都快不知道了……我只知道我搞砸了……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你聽完……也覺得我很可惡吧……？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……的確很可惡。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈哈……果然……那也沒關係，我早就做好抱著罪惡感活一輩子的覺悟……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嗚啊！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punchs", "連續拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我是你唯一的懺悔對象吧？你需要抱有罪惡感的人只有我。我剛剛聽完這些覺得很不爽，現在揍了你一頓，覺得超爽的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這樣就扯平了。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……哈？喂，你答應過我做你認為正確的決定的……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯，我做了。如果以後想起這些還很不爽的話我隨時會再揍你，代替那些因為你而遭遇不幸的人。你就乖乖閉嘴給我揍。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈……這就是我受到的制裁嗎？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「地下制裁者」，你不是希望我再做嗎？我回來了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈……輸給你……話說回來你這是什麼拳頭啊？根本不痛不癢。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那我再多給你幾拳好了？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……不，不用了……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……JOE，你剛剛提到的人口販賣，有個叫「Ringo」的小女孩對吧？那剛好跟我現在在查的案子有關。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "真的嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯，我思考了一下……你跟 Baro 黑幫的處境，以我現在的立場很難做些什麼，他們實在太龐大了……\n不過至少這個小女孩的案子我可以先幫忙破。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你要怎麼做？Diego 他們藏得很好，消息一走漏馬上就會聯想到我這裡來……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "放心，「X」回來了。交給我吧，不會牽連到你的。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Simon，謝謝你。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "什麼啊？不像你啊，而且我現在隨時有免費的拳頭可以揮在你身上，別謝得太早。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不，真的很謝謝你……我一直以來被壓力壓得快喘不過氣了，好像被惡魔掐著心臟一樣……變得歇斯底里的……我媽也很擔心我。這樣說出來後真的好多了……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃啊！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這拳是「不客氣」。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……你真的該多運動了。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "閉嘴。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……對了，那你說……大姐頭的事情可能跟我說的這些有關，這是怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯……Sherry、Luis、Shannon……還有我爸的死，可能都跟這個人口走私集團有關。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我後來查到了，這是一個在 Node 03 根深蒂固好幾十年的老組織了，好像叫「土竜」，可能連 03 的管理局都被他們滲透了……人口販賣是他們最大的生意之一。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你說大姐頭該不會……？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我說說我的看法吧……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Xenon_Studio", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "여긴 어디지?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Cafe의 지하실......「교역소」라고 불리는 곳이야.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Simon, 지금부터 내가 이곳에서 했던 모든 일들을... 네게 얘기해주마.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...그래. 말해봐.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "...사실 영감은 예전에...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "...이렇게 된 것이었어. 모든 거래는 바로 이곳에서 이루어졌지. 이 카페는 지금까지도 계속, 검은 조직들 사이에서 운영되면서 같은 서비스를 제공하고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "나는 줄곧 이 사실을 털어놓을 상대가 없었어. 영감은 이 가게를 내게 맡겼고 나는 영감의 사상에 동의했었어..... 그런데 어느 순간 이게 참회를 해야 할 일인지 아닌지도 모르게 돼버렸어.... 아는 것이라곤 내가 아주 큰일에 휘말려 버렸다는 사실뿐이었어....\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "다 듣고 나니..... 나, 아주 최악이지?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "....확실히 최악이다.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "하하....역시.... 그래도 상관없어. 그런 죄책감을 갖고 살게 될 것이라는 각오는 이미 오래전부터 해왔으니깐.....\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "으악!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punchs", "연속으로 주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "크헉!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "내가 네 유일한 참회 대상이었냐? 네놈에게 죄책감을 갖게 한 사람 역시 나밖에 없었던 거냐? 방금 얘기를 다 듣고 나서 기분이 더러웠는데, 이렇게라도 패고 나니깐 그나마 좀 나아지는 것 같군.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "이렇게 퉁 치자고.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......응? 이봐, 네가 옳다고 생각하는 대로 정확한 결정을 내리기로 약속 했...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "응, 이미 내렸어. 앞으로 이 일이 생각나서 기분이 더러워질 때마다 네놈을 패버리기로 했다. 너로 인해 불행해진 사람들을 생각해서도 그렇게 할 생각이다. 네 녀석은 입 다물고 나한테 얻어 맞기나 하라고.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "하.... 이것에 내가 받는 벌인가?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「어둠의 퍼니셔」 다시 해볼 생각 없냐고 물었지? 지금 돌아왔다.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "하하하.....역시 이길 수 없겠다니깐..... 근데 말이야 네놈, 주먹이 왜 그렇게 물렁해? 하나도 안 아프다고.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그래?\n그럼 몇 대 더 맞아도 상관 없겠군?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "....아, 아니... 사양하마....\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......JOE, 네가 조금 전에 말했던 인신매매 말이다... 거기에 「Ringo」라고 이름의 소녀가 있었다고 했지? 마침 내가 조사하고 있는 것과 관련이 있어.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "그게 정말이야!?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그래. 다시 정리해보면....너와 Baro파의 상황으로 볼 때, 지금 내가 개입해서 뭘 해볼 수 없는 입장일 것 같다. 그들은 엄청나게 큰 조직이야....\n그래도 최소한 이 소녀에 관한 일들은 먼저 해결할 수 있도록 도와주겠어.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "어떻게 할 생각이지? \nDiego는 숨기는 데 도가 튼 놈이라고. 게다가 소식이 새어나가면 바로 나부터 의심할 텐데......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "안심해. 「X」가 돌아왔으니, 내게 맡기라고. 어떻게든 네가 연루되지 않도록 할 생각이니깐.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......Simon, 고맙다.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "뭐? 네놈 답지 않군. 어쨌든 난, 언제든지 무료로 패버릴 수 있는 인간 샌드백이 있는 셈이니, 너무 그렇게 고마워할 필요 없다고.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "아니, 진심으로 고맙다....... 난 계속 그 엄청난 압박감 속에서 숨도 못 쉬고 살아왔어. 악마가 내 몸으로 들어와 심장을 누르고 있는 것처럼... 히스테리적으로 변해버리고 말이야.... 우리 엄마도 날 많이 걱정하시고 있거든. \n이렇게 전부 털어놓으니 그나마 좀 나아진 기분이 든다........\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "으악!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "방금 것은 「천만에」라는 대답이었어.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": ".....그런데 너, 정말 운동 좀 해야겠다.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "닥쳐.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "....그렇군.\n여두목의 일들과 내가 말했던 그 일들이 관련이 있을 거라고 말했었지? 그건 대체 어떻게 된 일이지?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "음...... Sherry, Luis, Shannon.... 그리고 내 아버지의 죽음. 이건 모두 그 인신매매단과 관련이 있어.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "뭐!?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "이 조직은 Node 03에서 뿌리 뽑히지 않은 채 수십 년간 유지되고 있는 조직이라는 정보를 찾아냈어. 그 단체의 이름은 「토룡(土竜)」. 03의 관리국도 이미 그들에게 물들어 있을 거야..... 인신매매는 그들이 하는 주요 사업 중 하나이기도 하고.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "네가 여두목은 아닐 거라고....?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......지금부터 내 생각을 말해주겠다....\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Xenon_Studio", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這是什麼地方？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Cafe 的地下室……俗稱「交易所」。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Simon，現在開始，我會把所有我在這裡做過的事情，都告訴你。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……嗯，說吧。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……其實老爹以前……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……就是這樣，所有的交易都是在這裡發生的。一直到現在，這間咖啡廳也還以相同的功用在黑幫間運作著……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我一直沒有能懺悔的對象，事業是老爹交給我的，我也認同他的理念……甚至連這本身是不是件該懺悔的事都快不知道了……我只知道我搞砸了……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你聽完……也覺得我很可惡吧……？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……的確很可惡。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈哈……果然……那也沒關係，我早就做好抱著罪惡感活一輩子的覺悟……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嗚啊！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punchs", "連續拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我是你唯一的懺悔對象吧？你需要抱有罪惡感的人只有我。我剛剛聽完這些覺得很不爽，現在揍了你一頓，覺得超爽的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這樣就扯平了。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……哈？喂，你答應過我做你認為正確的決定的……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯，我做了。如果以後想起這些還很不爽的話我隨時會再揍你，代替那些因為你而遭遇不幸的人。你就乖乖閉嘴給我揍。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈……這就是我受到的制裁嗎？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「地下制裁者」，你不是希望我再做嗎？我回來了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈……輸給你……話說回來你這是什麼拳頭啊？根本不痛不癢。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那我再多給你幾拳好了？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……不，不用了……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……JOE，你剛剛提到的人口販賣，有個叫「Ringo」的小女孩對吧？那剛好跟我現在在查的案子有關。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "真的嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯，我思考了一下……你跟 Baro 黑幫的處境，以我現在的立場很難做些什麼，他們實在太龐大了……\n不過至少這個小女孩的案子我可以先幫忙破。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你要怎麼做？Diego 他們藏得很好，消息一走漏馬上就會聯想到我這裡來……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "放心，「X」回來了。交給我吧，不會牽連到你的。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Simon，謝謝你。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "什麼啊？不像你啊，而且我現在隨時有免費的拳頭可以揮在你身上，別謝得太早。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不，真的很謝謝你……我一直以來被壓力壓得快喘不過氣了，好像被惡魔掐著心臟一樣……變得歇斯底里的……我媽也很擔心我。這樣說出來後真的好多了……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃啊！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這拳是「不客氣」。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……你真的該多運動了。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "閉嘴。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……對了，那你說……大姐頭的事情可能跟我說的這些有關，這是怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯……Sherry、Luis、Shannon……還有我爸的死，可能都跟這個人口走私集團有關。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我後來查到了，這是一個在 Node 03 根深蒂固好幾十年的老組織了，好像叫「土竜」，可能連 03 的管理局都被他們滲透了……人口販賣是他們最大的生意之一。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你說大姐頭該不會……？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我說說我的看法吧……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Xenon_Studio", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "这是什么地方？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Cafe 的地下室……俗称「交易所」。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Simon，现在开始，我会把所有我在这里做过的事情，都告诉你。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……嗯，说吧。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……其实老爹以前……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……就是这样，所有的交易都是在这里发生的。一直到现在，这间咖啡厅也还以相同的功用在黑帮间运作着……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我一直没有能忏悔的对象，事业是老爹交给我的，我也认同他的理念……甚至连这本身是不是件该忏悔的事都快不知道了……我只知道我搞砸了……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你听完……也觉得我很可恶吧……？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……的确很可恶。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈哈……果然……那也没关系，我早就做好抱着罪恶感活一辈子的觉悟……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呜啊！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punchs", "连续拳击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我是你唯一的忏悔对象吧？你需要抱有罪恶感的人只有我。我刚刚听完这些觉得很不爽，现在揍了你一顿，觉得超爽的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "这样就扯平了。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……哈？喂，你答应过我做你认为正确的决定的……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯，我做了。如果以后想起这些还很不爽的话我随时会再揍你，代替那些因为你而遭遇不幸的人。你就乖乖闭嘴给我揍。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈……这就是我受到的制裁吗？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「地下制裁者」，你不是希望我再做吗？我回来了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈……输给你……话说回来你这是什么拳头啊？根本不痛不痒。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那我再多给你几拳好了？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……不，不用了……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……JOE，你刚刚提到的人口贩卖，有个叫「Ringo」的小女孩对吧？那刚好跟我现在在查的案子有关。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "真的吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯，我思考了一下……你跟 Baro 黑帮的处境，以我现在的立场很难做些什么，他们实在太庞大了……\n不过至少这个小女孩的案子我可以先帮忙破。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你要怎么做？ Diego 他们藏得很好，消息一走漏马上就会联想到我这里来……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "放心，「X」回来了。交给我吧，不会牵连到你的。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……Simon，谢谢你。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "什么啊？不像你啊，而且我现在随时有免费的拳头可以挥在你身上，别谢得太早。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不，真的很谢谢你……我一直以来被压力压得快喘不过气了，好像被恶魔掐着心脏一样……变得歇斯底里的……我妈也很担心我。这样说出来后真的好多了……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃啊！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "这拳是「不客气」。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……你真的该多运动了。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "闭嘴。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……对了，那你说……大姐头的事情可能跟我说的这些有关，这是怎么回事？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯……Sherry、Luis、Shannon……还有我爸的死，可能都跟这个人口走私集团有关。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦！ ？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我后来查到了，这是一个在 Node 03 根深蒂固好几十年的老组织了，好像叫「土竜」，可能连 03 的管理局都被他们渗透了……人口贩卖是他们最大的生意之一。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你说大姐头该不会……？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我说说我的看法吧……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}